Description:
You arrive at a small village of lizardmen that seems almost empty, a lizardman approaches you and says:

"Sss... we don't want any trouble, right now our tribe and our leader are fighting on the eastern battlefield. If you want we could use a little help.

If you go south... sss... I have some items that may interest you, like this homemade slime bait that I am selling you for 400g or this hammer and nails for 300g, you can have both for 600g."
